          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If the file is extended (if ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "offset",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " is beyond the current end of file), the added characters are null bytes.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "This method raises ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsexceptionname/1415432-filehandleoperationexception",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": " if called on a file handle representing a pipe or socket, if the file descriptor is closed, or if the operation failed.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
